# SDD ephemeral planning — decision deferred until first archive completes.
# Do NOT gitignore openspec/changes/ yet; current cycle history must remain traceable.

# Force tracking of .atl/ and openspec/ despite the global ~/.config/git/ignore rules.
# These directories are load-bearing methodology artifacts in this project (skill
# registry + SDD change spool). The global ignore treats them as ephemeral, which
# is not true here.
!.atl/
!.atl/**
!openspec/
!openspec/**

# The local skill-registry cache is machine-specific, do not track it.
.atl/.skill-registry.cache.json
